---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Artem Shmatko" description="Computer scientist exploring the intersection of AI and computational biology">
	<header class="mb-16">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-normal mb-4 text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Welcome</h1>
		<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-2">
			Computer scientist exploring the intersection of AI and computational biology.
		</p>
		<p class="text-lg text-gray-500 leading-relaxed italic">
			Passionate about understanding intelligence, life, and the patterns that connect them.
		</p>
	</header>

	<div class="space-y-8">
		<section>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-normal mb-4 text-indigo-800">About</h2>
			<div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
				<p>
					My research interests lie in large-scale medical predictive systems and computational pathology, with particular focus on real-world applications beyond curated datasets. I'm especially interested in model generalisability, synthetic data generation, and pioneering solutions in emerging fields.
				</p>
				<p>
					Currently pursuing my PhD at Heidelberg University while working as a Visiting Scientist at the European Bioinformatics Institute. When I'm not immersed in research, I enjoy astrophotography, scuba diving, and reading science fiction.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-normal mb-4 text-indigo-800">Recent Work</h2>
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<div class="border-l-2 border-indigo-200 pl-6 py-3">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800">Generative Transformers for Disease History</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2">European Bioinformatics Institute • 2024</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700">Designing custom transformer models that estimate future disease risk based on medical history, surpassing traditional clinical approaches.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="border-l-2 border-indigo-200 pl-6 py-3">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800">Brain Tumour Classification</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-2">German Cancer Research Center • 2021-2025</p>
					<p class="text-gray-700">Developing transformer-based SOTA models for computational histopathology across seven countries, targeting direct clinical application.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-normal mb-4 text-indigo-800">Get in Touch</h2>
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<div class="flex justify-center space-x-8">
					<a 
						href="https://x.com/artem_shmatko"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors duration-200"
						title="@artem_shmatko"
					>
						<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
						</svg>
					</a>

					<a 
						href="https://github.com/yozhikoff"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors duration-200"
						title="GitHub: yozhikoff"
					>
						<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.30.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
						</svg>
					</a>

					<a 
						href="https://scholar.google.co.uk/citations?user=UXQl-IwAAAAJ&hl=en"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors duration-200"
						title="Google Scholar"
					>
						<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path d="M12 24a7 7 0 1 1 0-14 7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0-24L0 9.5l4.838 3.94A8.97 8.97 0 0 1 12 9a8.97 8.97 0 0 1 7.162 4.44L24 9.5z"/>
						</svg>
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="text-center">
					<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
						Want to chat? Twitter is your best bet! I'm always up for conversations about computational biology, AI research, the latest sci-fi novels, or pretty much anything that sparks curiosity. Don't worry about being too formal — I'm just a curious human who loves connecting with other curious humans. ✨
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>
